title: Daphne_ROMs_Complete
description:
Here are all the ROMs for the DAPHNE laserdisc arcade games.  These are 
just the ROMs from the machines' control boards.  The content of the 
laserdiscs must be obtained elsewhere.  Some of these games might not 
yet be fully supported by DAPHNE.
